#
# Every change to this repository must be reviewed and approved by Anne
# before merge. The pattern below makes Anne the default reviewer on
# every PR.
#
# This file alone does NOT block merges. To enforce blocking, an admin
# must enable the following in repo Settings → Branches → Branch
# protection rule for `main`:
#
#   - Require a pull request before merging
#   - Require approvals: 1
#   - Require review from Code Owners
#   - Dismiss stale pull request approvals when new commits are pushed
